# VHS Tape for devflow update
# Updates AI instructions and configuration
# Run with: vhs demos/setup/update.tape

Output demos/setup/update.gif
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Sleep 1s

# Show the command
Type "devflow update"
Enter
Sleep 2s

# Show update check
Sleep 1.5s

# Confirm update
Enter
Sleep 2s

# Show result
Sleep 3s
